{"type":"message","id":"b916fbc5","parentId":"98f0c548","timestamp":"2026-05-04T17:00:25.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the \"refurbished iPhone 6s\" search results. There are only 184 results (compared to 20,000 for just \"iPhone 6s\"). Looking at the results:\n\n1. CellphoneMall Phone Screen Protector 10 PCS Professional LCD Screen Protector for Refurbished iPhone 5 & 5S & 5C - ₹6,239 (this is a screen protector, not the phone)\n2. Samsung Galaxy S26 5G - ₹79,999 (irrelevant result)\n3. M Cart Silicone Soft Back Cover Case for Apple iPhone 6 / iPhone 6s (White) - ₹109\n4. TheGiftKart Sleek Back Cover Case for iPhone 6 / 6s - ₹249\n5. Amazon Brand - Solimo Back Cover for Apple iPhone 6 / iPhone 6S - ₹197.80\n6. SKP Microfiber Candy Back Cover Case for iPhone 6, iPhone 6S - (price not shown in truncated output)\n\nEven searching for \"refurbished iPhone 6s\" is still showing mostly accessories. The iPhone 6s is simply not available on Amazon India anymore - it's too old (released in 2015, discontinued years ago).\n\nLet me provide a clear summary to the user with what I found.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"I found the search results for \"refurbished iPhone 6s\" (only 184 results vs 20,000+ for \"iPhone 6s\"). Even here, most listings are **accessories**, not actual phones. Let me scroll to check if any actual phone listings exist:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_fKDTCEbavmtM0Dg1gim8s27T","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"marine-coral"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":64247,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777914017518,"responseId":"msg_2QW4FXtmVZ1jl0ZKRCllr2mb"}}
