{"type":"message","id":"ed9407e3","parentId":"3dad2616","timestamp":"2026-05-04T17:43:24.504Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-05-04 23:13 GMT+5:30] RamuKaka, Can you create a GanguBhai agent which can perform the Web Testing, another agent Chotu agent which can act as a Mobile Tester, Munna as a Performance Tester, PostmanKaka as an API Tester agent. Please create a dashboard which I am going to give you; its like a mission control where every agent is present and I can see who is working and who is not working. I want you to also create a way where if I give instruction to RamuKaka, Ramukaka will divide the instruction between the family, between the sub agents. For Example, RamuKaka will first of all figure it out which project we are working on . For Example, we are working on app.vwo.com, from this GanguBhai will start creating testplan for web application: app.vwo.com, where as chotu who is a mobile tester will create testplan for the mobile testing,PostmanKaka will create test plan for api testing. Everything will be available on the dashboard, what exactly they are doing. Make sure every agent talk to each other and gives the feedback among them. Create a beautiful dashboard. I am going to give you reference as well where it will be a simple dashboard where in the right side as a side column we can see the agents, what are the tasks they are doing and activity log.\nI have attached the screenshot of the dashboard reference which you have to create, make sure you change the names and add proper icons for the family. Make sure they can communicate with each other and every agent has a seperate identity,memory and the soul"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/png"}],"timestamp":1777916603794}}
