{"type":"message","id":"d808a374","parentId":"9191f489","timestamp":"2026-05-04T18:12:22.376Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HTTP server is running. Now I should tell the user they can access it at http://localhost:8080/index.html","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **Dashboard is now LIVE!**\n\n### 🔗 Access URL:\n```\nhttp://localhost:8080/index.html\n```\n\n**Open that URL in your browser** to see the Testing Family Mission Control!\n\n---\n\n## 🖥️ What You'll See\n\n1. **Top Bar** - Testing Family logo + \"Deploy All\" button\n2. **Left Sidebar** - Navigation + Family Members list\n3. **Center Panel** - Agent status cards for each family member:\n   - 🕸️ **GanguBhai** (Web Tester) - Tests: 0 | Passed: 0 | Failed: 0\n   - 📱 **Chotu** (Mobile Tester) - Tests: 0 | Devices: 0 | Issues: 0\n   - ⚡ **Munna** (Performance) - RPS: 0 | Latency: 0ms | Uptime: 100%\n   - 📮 **PostmanKaka** (API Tester) - APIs: 0 | Passed: 0 | Failed: 0\n\n4. **Right Panel** - Live Activity Feed showing all actions\n5. **Communication Panel** - Family chat channel\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Quick Demo\n\nWant to see it in action? Try this in your browser console (F12 → Console tab):\n\n```javascript\ncoordinateTest(\"https://app.vwo.com\")\n```\n\nThis will simulate RamuKaka assigning tasks to the entire family for testing app.vwo.com!\n\nLet me know if you can see the dashboard or if you need help with anything! 🕸️📱⚡📮🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":69136,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777918332620,"responseId":"msg_BZVWnDeYcSKeKIlRXZpR4IwK"}}
